sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: ArchiveTask
    C->>A: ArchiveTask(taskId)
    A->>PM: ArchiveTask(taskId)
    PM->>PM: GetTasks() [verify task exists & is "done"]
    PM->>PA: ArchiveTask(taskId)
    PA->>PA: os.Rename(done/{id}.json -> archived/{id}.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(old+new) -> Commit()
    PM->>PM: removeFromTaskOrder([taskId])
    PM->>PA: SaveTaskOrder(filtered)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: ArchiveAllDoneTasks
    C->>A: ArchiveAllDoneTasks()
    A->>PM: ArchiveAllDoneTasks()
    PM->>PM: GetTasks()
    loop For each task with status "done"
        PM->>PM: ArchiveTask(taskId)
    end
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: RestoreTask
    C->>A: RestoreTask(taskId)
    A->>PM: RestoreTask(taskId)
    PM->>PA: RestoreTask(taskId)
    PA->>PA: os.Rename(archived/{id}.json -> done/{id}.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(old+new) -> Commit()
    PM->>PA: LoadTaskOrder()
    PM->>PM: Append taskId to "done" zone
    PM->>PA: SaveTaskOrder(orderMap)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: ReorderTasks
    C->>A: ReorderTasks(positions)
    A->>PM: ReorderTasks(positions)
    PM->>PA: LoadTaskOrder()
    PM->>PM: Merge proposed positions into full order map
    PM->>PA: SaveTaskOrder(mergedMap)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: ReorderResult{Success, Positions}
    A-->>C: *ReorderResult

    Note over C,R: ProcessPriorityPromotions
    C->>A: ProcessPriorityPromotions()
    A->>PM: ProcessPriorityPromotions()
    PM->>PM: GetTasks() [all tasks]
    loop For each task with promotionDate <= today & priority = important-not-urgent
        PM->>PM: Promote to important-urgent, clear promotionDate
        alt Zone change needed
            PM->>PA: UpdateTaskWithOrderMove(task, oldZone, newZone)
            PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
        else Same zone
            PM->>PA: SaveTask(task)
            PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
        end
    end
    PM-->>A: []PromotedTask
    A-->>C: []PromotedTask
